OL,3,CTrump to raise 'everything' with King,
OL,4,Cincluding Iran war that has hit
OL,5,Crelations
OL,7,FDonald Trump has said he plans to talk
OL,8,Fto the King about "everything" during
OL,9,Fthe royal state visit, including the
OL,10,FIran war which has strained
OL,11,Ftransatlantic relations.
OL,13,FThe US president also said he would
OL,14,Fraise the thorny issue of Nato, which
OL,15,Fhe has lambasted throughout the
OL,16,Fconflict.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@^O]
