PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777158180
OL,3,CTrump to raise 'everything' with King,
OL,4,Cincluding Iran war that has hit
OL,5,Crelations
OL,7,FThe American leader made his comments
OL,8,Fto Reuters as fresh controversy flared
OL,9,Fover reports the US could review its
OL,10,Fposition on Britain's claim to the
OL,11,FFalkland Islands as punishment for Sir
OL,12,FKeir Starmer's lack of support for the
OL,13,Fmilitary action against Tehran.
OL,15,FThe latest dispute comes just days
OL,16,Fbefore the King and Queen arrive in
OL,17,Fthe US for a four-day state visit to
OL,18,Fmark the 250th anniversary of US
OL,19,Findependence from Britain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777158180
OL,3,CTrump to raise 'everything' with King,
OL,4,Cincluding Iran war that has hit
OL,5,Crelations
OL,7,FAs well as meeting with Mr Trump, the
OL,8,Froyal couple will be guests of honour
OL,9,Fat a White House banquet and the
OL,10,Fmonarch has been invited to address a
OL,11,Fjoint meeting of the US Congress.
OL,13,FIn addition Charles and Camilla will
OL,14,Falso visit Virginia and New York.
OL,16,FMr Trump said: "I'm going to talk
OL,17,Fabout everything."
OL,26,@xD@POUyD@RO]
