OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777158180
OL,3,CTrump to raise 'everything' with King,
OL,4,Cincluding Iran war that has hit
OL,5,Crelations
OL,7,FAmong other topics he was set to raise
OL,8,Fwith the King was the UK's digital
OL,9,Fservices tax on American social media
OL,10,Ffirms.
OL,12,FThe president has threatened to impose
OL,13,Fa "big tariff" on Britain unless it
OL,14,Fdrops the 2% levy on the revenues of
OL,15,Fseveral major US tech companies.
OL,17,FThe tax targets companies whose
OL,18,Fworldwide revenues from digital
OL,19,Factivities exceed #500 million, with
OL,20,Fmore than #25 million of the revenue
OL,21,Ffrom UK users.
OL,26,@uD@COUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
