PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777158180
OL,3,CTrump to raise 'everything' with King,
OL,4,Cincluding Iran war that has hit
OL,5,Crelations
OL,7,FAccording to a 2025 Treasury review,
OL,8,Fthe levy raised more than #800 million
OL,9,Fin 2024`25, up from #678 million in
OL,10,F2023`24.
OL,12,FMr Trump has previously said that the
OL,13,Froyal trip could "absolutely" mend
OL,14,Frelations with the UK and hailed the
OL,15,FKing a "great man".
OL,17,FThis is in stark contrast to his view
OL,18,Fof the UK Prime Minister, who he has
OL,19,Fderided as weak and indecisive.
OL,26,@uD@ROUuD@]O]wD@HOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
