OL,3,CTrump to raise 'everything' with King,
OL,4,Cincluding Iran war that has hit
OL,5,Crelations
OL,7,FTensions show no sign of abating as US
OL,8,Fdefence secretary Pete Hegseth
OL,9,Fdismissed efforts being led by the UK
OL,10,Fand France to ensure the future
OL,11,Fsecurity of the Strait of Hormuz as
OL,12,F"silly".
OL,14,FHe argued Europe should start having
OL,15,F"less fancy conferences and get in a
OL,16,Fboat", as he rebuked Britain and other
OL,17,Fcountries for their response to the
OL,18,Fcrisis in the critical Gulf waterway.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@GO]wD@AOUxD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
