OL,3,CTrump to raise 'everything' with King,
OL,4,Cincluding Iran war that has hit
OL,5,Crelations
OL,7,FIn pointed comments, Mr Hegseth said
OL,8,FAmerica deserved allies "who are
OL,9,Floyal" and understood the partnership
OL,10,Fwas "not a one-way street".
OL,12,FThe strait, which is a major supply
OL,13,Froute for oil and gas supplies, had
OL,14,Fbeen open prior to the US and Israel
OL,15,Flaunching strikes against Iran.
OL,17,FIn retaliation, Tehran effectively
OL,18,Fclosed the shipping lane.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@FO]rD@EOUrD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
