SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777158180
OL,3,CTrump to raise 'everything' with King,
OL,4,Cincluding Iran war that has hit
OL,5,Crelations
OL,7,FAnd although Mr Trump extended an
OL,8,Funeasy ceasefire, the strategic
OL,9,Fshipping lane remains a flashpoint,
OL,10,Fwith both the US and Iran imposing
OL,11,Ftheir own blockades, bringing the
OL,12,Fmovement of vessels to a virtual
OL,13,Fstandstill, further fuelling a global
OL,14,Fenergy crisis that has seen prices
OL,15,Frocket.
OL,17,FHowever, hopes have been raised of
OL,18,Ftalks to resolve the conflict, with US
OL,19,Fspecial envoys Steve Witkoff and Jared
OL,20,FKushner being sent to Pakistan on
OL,21,FSaturday "to hear the Iranians out".
OL,26,@}D@JOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
