PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777158180
OL,3,CTrump to raise 'everything' with King,
OL,4,Cincluding Iran war that has hit
OL,5,Crelations
OL,7,FIranian foreign minister Abbas
OL,8,FAraghchi is currently in Islamabad,
OL,9,Falthough Foreign Ministry spokesman
OL,10,FEsmael Baqaei said on X that "no
OL,11,Fmeeting is planned to take place
OL,12,Fbetween Iran and the US".
OL,14,FHe said officials from Pakistan would
OL,15,Fconvey messages between the two sides.
OL,17,FBut White House press secretary
OL,18,FKaroline Leavitt said: "We're hopeful
OL,19,Fthat it will be a productive
OL,20,Fconversation and hopefully move the
OL,21,Fball forward to a deal.
OL,26,@rD@^OUtD@XO]zD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
