CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777158180
OL,3,CTrump to raise 'everything' with King,
OL,4,Cincluding Iran war that has hit
OL,5,Crelations
OL,7,F"We've certainly seen some progress
OL,8,Ffrom the Iranian side in the last
OL,9,Fcouple of days."
OL,11,FWhile vice president JD Vance was not
OL,12,Fgoing, Ms Leavitt said he and
OL,13,Fsecretary of state Marco Rubio were on
OL,14,F"standby" to fly to Pakistan "if
OL,15,Fnecessary".
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@PO]vD@AOUvD@IO]vD@^OUwD@JO]
